snippet.description:
In this video, we are going to discuss is amber heard going to be the highest-paid actress in Hollywood.

When James Wan dropped the official title of Aquaman 2, it was quickly overshadowed by further calls for star Amber Heard to be fired by those who were still unhappy with her domestic violence allegations against her ex-husband Johnny. Depp. With an online petition of more than 1.85 million signatures demanding that Heard be removed from the sequel, you'd think Warner Bros. Justice League. But if there is a new whisper in the industry to believe, not only does Warner Bros. not care, but they are about to do something that will further enrage Heard's foes.
